FBIS3-52965 "drnes007dd_94002" FBIS-NES-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 Palestinian Affairs 'Arafat Said To Divert Funds To Fight Factions NC1101084294 Beirut AL-'AHD in Arabic 31 Dec 93 p 22 NC1101084294 Beirut AL-'AHD Language: Arabic Article Type:BFN [Text] Palestinian circles have revealed that 95 Palestinian embassies are suffering financial crises and only small amounts of the funding they require are being transferred to them. The circles say that an unannounced decision by 'Arafat stipulated that financial allocations for these embassies should be cut so that the funds can be invested in European banks and used for fighting internal battles with the opposition Palestinian factions.
